{"questionId": "555c176c-fa9a-40e0-b8a8-cb40b47c9ee3_22", "correctAnswer": "1/12,.0833", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Vieta shortcut: sum of solutions $= -b/a$", "content": "For $24x^2 - (12a + 2b)x + ab = 0$, identify $A = 24$, $B = -(12a+2b)$.<br/>$$\\text{sum} = -\\frac{B}{A} = \\frac{12a+2b}{24}$$"}, {"title": "Factor and match to $k(6a+b)$", "content": "$$\\frac{12a+2b}{24} = \\frac{2(6a+b)}{24} = \\frac{6a+b}{12} = \\frac{1}{12}(6a+b)$$<br/>So $k = \\dfrac{1}{12}$. That matches choice 1/12 — <strong>1/12</strong> is correct."}]}
